headline: Country Music Star Dierks Bentley Signs on to Support 2026 Special Olympics Airlift, Inspiring Pilots Nationwide to Answer the Call
summary: WICHITA, Kan., September 04, 2025--Multi-platinum country music artist Dierks Bentley has officially pledged his support for the 2026 Special Olympics Airlift.
